##Vernal Equinox: Flowers in full bloom, people have feelings

Micro-signal Yeguangbeifukan

Function introduction the supplement of Xinmin Evening News, founded on May 1,1946, is the oldest comprehensive supplement of Chinese newspapers.

Tomorrow at the Spring Equinox. This spring is special, the cherry blossom, the sweet smell in the air, these beautiful things bring comfort, we love life more than ever.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The first sign of spring is not the willow's hard branches covered with a veil of light smoke, or the flowerpot thrown on the balcony last year with a petite petit petit petit petit petit petit waist, it was as if someone had lifted the lid and the sun was pouring down from a great height. Suddenly I feel a little dizzy, like opening my eyes and finding myself in an elevator going up to the sky. At this time all kinds of birds also clear up, cooing, chirping, chirping, there are three syllables, four syllables... although do not understand, very beautiful, very tactful. Some trees have not a leaf, but the birds are not fastidious, shuttle up and down, blurred around, and in between the trees, trees and eaves, eaves and eaves, between countless air routes. Just stop for a minute and be drawn into this kaleidoscope of infinite riotous bustle. At this point YOU WILL SIGH: Spring!

I've never been a big believer in giving too much symbolism to spring, which has too much to bear. The Earth's orbit around the sun, and the slope of the Earth's axis of rotation, add heat to this monotonous circular motion (I imagine it is an orange paint brush) and the joy of painting back and forth between the tropic of Capricorn, giving rise to the seasons. Only the scribes with half-bottle of vinegar hanging from the penholder would make a fuss about it. In the evolution of billions of years, many living beings on earth have figured out the way to survive together with heat. Every life has its own life cycle, such as the forelock, the forelock and the forelock, the heat brush from afar, "by universal convention, " decodes each cycle, large and small. For Man it is another year, for the flower it is another life, for the bird it is another seventh of a life. Spring is a fleeting time, and the vision of the world can not depend on the beauty of one or two images.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
But this spring must be a special one, one that requires phenology. Let's not talk about anything else. Let's talk about my two friends. A friend, Yan Qing, was in Beijing, my father called from his hometown in Yingtan. "I finally got out of the neighborhood, and walked to the No Man's Land along the river. The Cherry blossoms filled the air with the sweet smell of honey. I wanted to share it with you, so I gave you a call. " She Hung Up, i'd like to go home, Florida, but I can't. Another friend of mine, Anqing, who used to live in Beijing to write, came back to visit her parents in Wuxue, Hubei Province for the Spring Festival, by the Riverside (coincidentally, there is also a river, where the Chinese people can not get rid of the word "Riverside") , the rape flowers are in full bloom, and the earth ears are in full bloom, "I heard firecrackers in the morning and went downstairs to ask my father. He said it was the flower festival. It was a flower-watching festival. Sure enough, I saw firecrackers and burning paper. In the afternoon, the first spring thunder sounded. It was time for spring ploughing. "

The Sun goes round and round, the time goes on, the beauty of spring —————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————— --.

One last thing I found. Recently, often wandering in the community flower path, accident is, Camellia, two leaf plum, Cherry, knot fragrance, Yingchun, and not more than in previous years, more exuberant, according to my expectations, no one disturb, vegetation spread, Haruhana should be more prosperous. In previous years, many people appreciate flowers, everywhere "flowers see crazy" , did not expect, flowers have no one to appreciate, but also no heart in full bloom. Do Flowers Get mad? Wait here.
